urdu transliteration text:
Sakina dekh rahi hai
Sakina is watching…
@HujjatELC

Wo zibha hote huwe baap ko na dekh sakeMeri sakina hai masoom ye khayaal rahe Sitam ye uspe na dhaana abhi churi na chalana, sakina dekh rahi hai
Please remember Sakina is very young and innocent,
@HujjatELC

Tumhaare laashaa-e be sar ko du(n) kafan kaiseMujhe bataao zara tum batool ke beteHai bekasi ka natija padha hai ret pe laasha, sakina dekh rahi hai
Sakina is watching
@HujjatELC
